                    <p class="date-updated">Apr 20, 2024</p>
                </div>
                <p>The Manila Clock Tower Museum is a historical landmark located in Manila City Hall. This iconic art deco structure houses a museum showcasing Manila's rich history through photographs, documents, and artifacts. The tower offers panoramic views of the city and features a working clock mechanism that has been ticking since 1940. Visitors can explore the history of Manila's governance and architecture while enjoying breathtaking views from the observation deck.</p>
            </section>

