                <h3 class="section-title">Highlights</h3>
                <ul class="highlights-list">
                    <li>Historic art deco architecture dating back to 1940</li>
                    <li>Panoramic observation deck with 360° views of Manila</li>
                    <li>Original clock mechanism still in operation</li>
                    <li>Exhibits on Manila's history and local government</li>
                    <li>Vintage photographs and historical documents</li>
                    <li>Free admission for all visitors</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

